Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.43,0:00:45.30,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,As I’m sure you know,\Nlife isn’t all sunshine and rainbows.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.30,0:00:50.94,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,Indeed, you too sometimes get\Nsad or tired, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.77,0:00:57.68,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,“Are There Any Tea Dogs\NWhere You Live?”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.51,0:01:06.12,Default,Mana's Mom,0,0,0,,Mana, you need to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.12,0:01:09.05,Default,Mana's Mom,0,0,0,,Dad can’t help it, he has work.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.05,0:01:10.79,Default,Mana's Mom,0,0,0,,Mana, get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.36,0:01:16.56,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,Mana loves her dad,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.56,0:01:20.70,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,but he’s always too busy\Nto be home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.67,0:01:24.44,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,Even today, on her birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.82,0:01:39.32,Default,Mana,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:41.19,Default,Mana,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.19,0:01:42.45,Default,Mana,0,0,0,,Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.36,0:01:54.40,Default,Mana's Mom,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.23,0:01:57.53,Default,Mana's Mom,0,0,0,,Mana, where were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.00,0:02:02.91,Default,Mana,0,0,0,,Mom, this puppy’s name is Ryoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.91,0:02:04.41,Default,Mana,0,0,0,,Can we keep him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.28,0:02:07.11,Default,Mana's Mom,0,0,0,,In our apartment, hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.71,0:02:16.02,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,Her mother was suddenly met\Nwith a wave of nostalgia,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.02,0:02:18.79,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,as if she'd seen this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.70,0:02:29.93,Default,Mana's Mom,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.93,0:02:33.17,Default,Mana's Mom,0,0,0,,We’ll ask Daddy about it\Nwhen he comes home, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.17,0:02:34.51,Default,Mana,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.51,0:02:35.51,Default,Sora,0,0,0,,Hey, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.37,0:02:39.74,Default,Mana,0,0,0,,Mom, Dad’s home!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.25,0:02:42.35,Default,Mana,0,0,0,,Big bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.72,0:02:49.42,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,Dad’s home even earlier than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.42,0:02:53.09,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,These tea dogs, soothing\Nthe hearts of tired humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.09,0:02:55.89,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,are certain to be found\Nwhere you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.89,0:02:58.36,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,There’s not one far from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.46,0:03:04.74,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,Sudden sadness or sudden tears
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.74,0:03:10.14,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,There’s someone nearby\NWaiting for you to notice
