Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.62,0:00:03.35,OP,Mitsuko Horie,0,0,0,,Cha-cha-cha-cha, cha-cha-cha-cha, Tea Dog
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.35,0:00:06.16,OP,Mitsuko Horie,0,0,0,,Come along with me (Oh yeah!)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.16,0:00:09.06,OP,Mitsuko Horie,0,0,0,,My little ray of sunshine (Let's go!)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.06,0:00:14.80,OP,Mitsuko Horie,0,0,0,,Run to me with a great big smile (All the way)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.80,0:00:17.74,OP,Mitsuko Horie,0,0,0,,When we're together (Oh yeah!)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.74,0:00:20.60,OP,Mitsuko Horie,0,0,0,,I feel so magical (Alright!)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.60,0:00:26.54,OP,Mitsuko Horie,0,0,0,,And so much warmer (Doo-doo-doo-doo)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.05,0:00:30.82,OP,Mitsuko Horie,0,0,0,,You little scamp, Tea Dog
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.82,0:00:33.42,OP,Mitsuko Horie,0,0,0,,My perky little Tea Dog
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.79,0:00:37.80,OP,Mitsuko Horie,0,0,0,,I L-O-V-E you, Tea Dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.56,0:03:12.38,ED,Morinoki Children,0,0,0,,Cha-cha-cha, cha-cha-cha
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:14.23,ED,Morinoki Children,0,0,0,,Tea Dogs, cha-cha-cha
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.23,0:03:17.77,ED,Morinoki Children,0,0,0,,Take a rice cake, stick a bean on it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.77,0:03:21.10,ED,Morinoki Children,0,0,0,,Give it two lil eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.57,0:03:25.27,ED,Morinoki Children,0,0,0,,Give it big leaves, paws, and a butt
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.27,0:03:28.63,ED,Morinoki Children,0,0,0,,Then its leaf tail, and you're all done

